## ğŸš€ Project Description
The Student Management API is a backend system that supports all operations required to run an academic institution efficiently.
It enables CRUD operations for students and teachers, course creation, enrollment logic, attendance tracking, grading, and authentication.

This API is built with **clean architecture**, follows **REST principles**, and is ready for deployment.

